quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,Ngwamba! Nguulumbila mwesi
  74,33,Ni chilo ndema jachikutyoka (pakucha)
  74,34,Ni kumasikusiku ndema jakukulanguka
  74,35,Chisimu Walakwe (Motowo) uŵele limpepe (m’makungu) gekulungwa nnope
  74,36,Chitetelo kwa ŵandu
  74,37,Kwa jwalijose mwa jenumanja jwaasachile kuti alongolele (pakutenda yambone) kapena kusigalila (pakupanganya yakusakala)
  74,38,Mundu jwalijose tachiŵa uwombosi wakuliombolela ku (yakusakala) yaŵapanganyisye (pakutaŵidwa ku Moto)
  74,39,Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵakunkono wan'dyo
  74,40,(Chachiŵa) m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo achiwuusyanaga
  74,41,Ya (ŵandu) ŵakuleŵa
  74,42,“Ana ni chichi chachin'jinjisye ŵanganyammwe ku Saqara?”
  74,43,"(Pakwanga) chachitiji: “Nganituŵa mwa akuswali.”"
  74,44,“Soni nganituŵa nkwaaliisya masikini.”
  74,45,“Ni twaliji nkutiŵila (mu sambi) pamo ni akutiŵila.”
  74,46,“Ni twaliji soni nkukanila ya Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  74,47,“Mpaka chatuichilile chiwa.”
  74,48,Basi ngasichija kwakamuchisya ŵanganyao chondechonde cha akuchondelela
  74,49,Ana chipali chichi kukwao chikwatendekasya kuchitundumalila chikumbusyo (Qur’an)
  74,50,(Kakwipuche kakwe kuti akajipikana Qur’an) gamba kuŵa ŵanganyao mpela mbunda (syamwitinji) syasikwipusyidwe
  74,51,Syasikutila lisimba
  74,52,Yeti mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao akusakaga ali apedwile ikalakala yeunukule-unukule (kuumila kwa Allah kutendela umboni yakuŵecheta Muhammadi ﷺ)
  74,53,Ngwamba! Nambo kuti ŵanganyao ngaakujijogopa Akhera
  74,54,Ngwamba! Chisimu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) jiŵele chikumbusyo
  74,55,Basi jwaakusaka taalikumbusye najo
  74,56,Ni nganaŵa alikumbwisye ŵanganyao ikaŵeje naga Allah ali asachile. Jwalakwe ni jwaali Jwakuŵajilwa kogopedwa soni ni Nysene chikululuko